Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,電的基本三法則
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,歐姆的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,雷壓=電流乘以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 歐姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,V=IR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,, 一定要記住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,v=IR 這是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 打開下 一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（謝謝今天的橡皮擦）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,（不客氣）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,（今天換夏裝怕忘記了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害羞 會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說不出口\N但對她的時尚敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沐浴露在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（制服美少女 鬼畜輪姦）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我們學校的制服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這樣的人嗎 有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真希 是她嗎 不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好累啊 圖書館就是涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,, 一這個是什麼啊\N 一這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,誰忘掉的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,, 一看看裡面吧 一可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦啦 有這個東西\N這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,衛生巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到更棒的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,, 一要看看嗎 一這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,, 一還有這個東西 一是誰的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,, 一很在意吧 一當然很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,, 一是真希的吧 一是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 看不出來的啊\N看起來這麼單純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,, 一沒想到有這個 一真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:06:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,, 一眼鏡摘了是不是很可愛啊\N 一有嗎 還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能愛上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你的興趣太奇怪了\N 一真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我交往好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（摘掉眼鏡很受歡迎\N我吃醋）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,（我只想一個人喜歡我）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（交往的話會被大家知道）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（還很討厭被告白）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,手機不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 有人嗎 開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我有話要說 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,, 一什麼話 一是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你都做過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 是那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我也做做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你囉嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼細小的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼細小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很輕的 你看吧\N隨便就抱起夾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真是超級有成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來吧 來啊\N 一不要 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道這裡沒人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,, 一沒有任何人的 一就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你派麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒事的哦 夾吧 趕緊來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好細小的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好小哦 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別說不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙也是這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我舔耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,, 一味道很不錯 一不要才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,脖子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我安靜點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了啊 給我按著\N奶子是什麼味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大腿不錯哦 滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看看什麼感覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來吧 一什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,, 一純色的\N 一原來如此啊 再看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 一不要才怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的屁股很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 趕緊來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,, 一腿抬起來我看看\N 一不要才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 就是這樣不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡凹陷進去了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是很有感覺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 你好色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 又羼透了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你在做什麼 別搞我\N 一別摸你才怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你其實是變態吧\N 一好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要啊 一不要才怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡欲求不滿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這次襖後面 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,, 對對對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣子來吧 對著我\N對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 太棒了 動起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來 脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很有感覺吧 對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續扭起來 對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,頂到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越有感覺了 你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,, 一全都看到了哦 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要才怪 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞的樣子好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,聞味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,味道好棒哦 我喜歡的\N香水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我來舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣啥服務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 你要舔的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快點看啊 如何啊 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一不要這樣\N 一不要才怪 什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不說不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼感學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,說了就放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要啊 一想直接舔裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,手放上面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好美的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好想看的啊 夾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛啊 安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼罩杯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼罩杯告訴我 他知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,的哦\N知道你\N的 一切\N是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,乳頭硬了 好可愛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看了 看清楚了 這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,經常被他舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,, 一才么有舔哦 一肯定有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯哦 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,, 一讓我舔個夠哦 一不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點 沒有人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,摸了沒有毛 為什麼沒有毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說你自己剃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要啊 一你有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸摸 顫抖哦 對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,, 一這樣才對 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你都濕透了啊 一沒有濕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看濕濕的小穴 起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 就是這樣 沒錯\N很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,, 一好厲害啊 軟軟的\N 一沒有陰毛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,軟較的 對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯啊 真好啊 再來\N不錯 不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 怎麼了有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫蕩的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,, 一跟他做夠了吧 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊 做過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,手指也插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來吧 一不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦 給我閉嘴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,騙子哦 來只有讓你更爽了\N起來 我舔你小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,腿抬起夾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯哦 沒錯的\N真是不錯 全看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:22:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,, 一手拿開哦\N這樣哦 好袖珍的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 菊花也看到了\N趕緊腿分開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,, 一舒服嗎 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 一不要才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,自己看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎 腿分開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你被他舔過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣很快就高潮了 這麼敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,, 一可以高潮的哦 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,別客氣 高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.05,0:23:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧 在顫枓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.64,0:24:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,佩濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.38,0:24:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了 好厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.55,0:24:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不妙了哦 小穴裡面\N 一你是妓女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.33,0:24:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.93,0:24:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看出來了 什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.84,0:24:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.45,0:24:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.32,0:25:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我舔了你 你也舔我的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.23,0:25:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,給我快點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.53,0:25:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來舔哦 快點哦\N 一真不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,, 一趕緊來舔啊哦\N 一你也舔過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.68,0:25:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.45,0:25:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊來舔 舒服點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.25,0:25:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,像你平時做的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.92,0:25:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他做的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.02,0:25:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我口交
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.79,0:25:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴張開 趕緊的\N嘴巴給我張開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.64,0:25:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.55,0:26:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴弄開 沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.92,0:26:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯的 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.83,0:26:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.23,0:26:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了哦 舔著也濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.38,0:26:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了呢 我也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.75,0:26:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.82,0:26:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.24,0:27:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.24,0:27:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微慢一點
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.11,0:27:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.11,0:27:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很舒服啊 有在舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.62,0:27:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.52,0:27:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.02,0:27:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.06,0:27:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.74,0:27:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續深深一點 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.45,0:27:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,含住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.79,0:27:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,給我好好含住了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.74,0:28:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,, 一好可愛 一小嘴巴好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.85,0:28:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,對對的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.23,0:28:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,, 一太棒了 一好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.20,0:28:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續 深一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.17,0:28:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,深一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.95,0:28:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,, 一好難受啊 一我會疼愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.62,0:29:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.23,0:29:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.23,0:29:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.67,0:29:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再深一點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.85,0:29:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.75,0:29:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.03,0:29:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好好接住
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.56,0:29:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.60,0:29:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來 快點 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.74,0:29:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.07,0:29:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,夾吧 要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.01,0:29:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出夾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.42,0:30:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊不
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.30,0:30:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.54,0:30:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧\N射出夾了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.55,0:30:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的套子再\N放到你的嘴巴里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我來代替你男友操你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.13,0:30:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你最近
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.20,0:30:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,應該要做愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.43,0:30:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還拿著套子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.14,0:31:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一你就是個碧池吧\N一我不是 還沒有跟他做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.05,0:31:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有做愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.72,0:31:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.52,0:31:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我運氣好啊 真是好啊\N很好就用那個套子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.03,0:31:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,來操你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.70,0:31:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來吧 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.87,0:31:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.94,0:31:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.61,0:31:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,腿分開
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.71,0:31:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,, 一沒錯 沒錯 很舒服的\N 一給我分開
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.25,0:31:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.62,0:31:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴也是濕透了 再來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.63,0:31:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.57,0:31:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊來哦 對的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.24,0:32:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我要進去了 一不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.54,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.35,0:32:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來吧 一我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.45,0:32:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.53,0:32:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.43,0:32:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 扭腰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.37,0:32:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.41,0:32:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.61,0:32:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的小穴 你也舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.78,0:32:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 救救我\N 一沒人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.92,0:32:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服麻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.49,0:32:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.16,0:32:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.53,0:33:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼感覺啊\N這個肉棒插進去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼感覺 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.94,0:33:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.41,0:33:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.21,0:33:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去了哦 沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.89,0:33:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.82,0:33:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.93,0:33:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.47,0:33:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.61,0:33:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 一小穴不錯哦 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.12,0:33:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 為什麼要操我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.32,0:34:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是因為你帶著套子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.33,0:34:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是個碧池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.63,0:34:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,, 一對對對的 一很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.14,0:34:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不是的 一沒錯繼續來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.11,0:34:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.85,0:34:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.12,0:34:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.56,0:34:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.53,0:34:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,, 一放開我 放我下來\N 一才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.63,0:35:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 太舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.70,0:35:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.04,0:35:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很舒服吧 對對 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.91,0:35:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.85,0:35:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續來操你 我讓你滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.99,0:35:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.52,0:35:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.68,0:36:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.21,0:36:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.73,0:36:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯哦 從後面來吧 屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.43,0:36:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,從後面插進去 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.24,0:36:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.33,0:36:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,後面很舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.36,0:36:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.94,0:37:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.43,0:37:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.04,0:37:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.49,0:37:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.83,0:38:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好不錯的哦 對對
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.03,0:38:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想射進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.12,0:38:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大棒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.43,0:38:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.75,0:38:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.32,0:38:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.32,0:39:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.22,0:39:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.33,0:39:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.23,0:39:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.64,0:39:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,, 一真不錯啊 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.47,0:39:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.34,0:39:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不錯哦 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.11,0:39:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.71,0:40:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.36,0:40:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.93,0:40:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.63,0:40:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.97,0:40:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.54,0:41:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,, 一怎麼了啊 一不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.75,0:41:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.92,0:41:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你表情就是要肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.02,0:41:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,淫蕩的表情 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.56,0:41:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.06,0:41:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.98,0:41:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.61,0:41:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個感覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.41,0:41:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.39,0:41:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.82,0:41:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,, 一來吧 一不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.23,0:41:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.84,0:42:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.55,0:42:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要啊 一我要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.92,0:42:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 不要 一我射了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.82,0:42:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 仔細看
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.03,0:42:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,射了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.52,0:42:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,, 一讓我看臉 一不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.13,0:42:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.80,0:43:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.53,0:43:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這個照片
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.53,0:43:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我就流傳出去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.24,0:43:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,, 一懂了吧 一不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.55,0:43:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,, 一怎麼了啊\N 一還想再做啊真的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.99,0:43:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.03,0:43:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.33,0:43:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.97,0:43:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.04,0:43:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,, 一早上好\N 一昨天抱歉說了一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.65,0:43:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困在更衣室\N手機也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.32,0:44:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是老師幫我開門 也行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.03,0:44:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.43,0:44:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,, 一老師昨天謝謝 一沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.73,0:44:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你是考試擔當 要準備一下\N 一好的 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.44,0:44:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.35,0:44:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你有游泳證嘛 一嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.65,0:44:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那你穿泳衣來泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.72,0:44:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是物理老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.13,0:44:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我們來實習 是給你的特訓\N 一給我的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.44,0:44:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.54,0:44:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.81,0:44:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.43,0:45:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是來了啊 真是身村纖細\N好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.64,0:45:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那個影片的肉棒好大啊\N雖然我不算太大
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.82,0:45:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的那個XS能插嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.90,0:45:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.14,0:45:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.84,0:46:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了影片
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.41,0:46:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,給我老實點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.70,0:46:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.84,0:46:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,泳衣真適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.04,0:46:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,轉過去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.55,0:46:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.72,0:46:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股好小 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.03,0:46:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼小的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.63,0:46:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.55,0:47:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.52,0:47:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了 這個小身體
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.72,0:47:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下插進去的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.93,0:47:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 不籬這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.44,0:47:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.85,0:47:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想像就勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.95,0:47:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.99,0:47:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快點來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.26,0:48:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.03,0:48:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要的表情反倒讓我興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.81,0:48:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.71,0:48:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,被那種肉棒插進去 很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.86,0:48:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.91,0:48:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感度正好
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.72,0:48:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,開始很疼 等下就熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.29,0:49:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.83,0:49:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.74,0:49:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,舉起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.01,0:49:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不能聞那裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.95,0:49:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我最喜歡味道了\N一好害羞啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.84,0:49:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.02,0:50:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.12,0:50:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要孺話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.62,0:50:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你說不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.43,0:50:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那個暴露就麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.93,0:50:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友你的爸媽
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.14,0:50:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有會被退學的 我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.32,0:50:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,KISS啊 搞不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.61,0:51:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出夾
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.35,0:51:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不舒服吧 要互相才舒服\N舌頭伸出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.96,0:51:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我還要
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.33,0:51:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.50,0:51:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我要唾液
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.37,0:52:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.38,0:52:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.32,0:52:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老師的大肉棒如何
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.03,0:52:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,變硬了啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.40,0:52:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,能插進你的XS小穴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.64,0:52:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 我會溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.15,0:52:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我很害怕的 一我會溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.26,0:52:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只要感受就好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.13,0:53:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去感受就不會疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.70,0:53:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.44,0:53:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.98,0:53:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.41,0:53:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看了那個影片 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.02,0:53:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有這麼可愛的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.50,0:54:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.83,0:54:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.80,0:54:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不能這麼摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.44,0:54:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,變舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.71,0:54:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.98,0:54:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我來讓你舒服 有感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.34,0:54:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.04,0:54:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.64,0:54:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.01,0:54:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真回愛
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.15,0:55:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.94,0:55:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不想停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.83,0:55:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.73,0:55:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜歡舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.93,0:55:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要好好舔年輕友孩
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.21,0:56:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股很敏感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.83,0:56:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.72,0:56:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了呢 有感覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.23,0:56:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕就很容易出汗\N那個味道真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.65,0:57:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也要舔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.54,0:57:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,乳頭 變硬了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.21,0:57:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,隔著泳衣我也感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.82,0:57:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.06,0:57:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,身體好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.52,0:58:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,乳頭勃起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.02,0:58:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.73,0:58:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要進犯你了 這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.43,0:58:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要開始搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.24,0:58:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.24,0:59:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 一真好吃啊 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.86,0:59:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.03,0:59:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不住了 跟學生比\N我的是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.54,0:59:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我說不出□
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.31,0:59:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要大肉棒對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.63,1:00:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.03,1:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.00,1:00:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴濕透了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.24,1:00:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.73,1:00:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這個小肉穴
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.23,1:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.47,1:00:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.94,1:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.84,1:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.05,1:01:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒要來了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.16,1:01:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.70,1:01:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,給我舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.83,1:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.74,1:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.51,1:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.69,1:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我要噴了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.69,1:02:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,給你弄滿
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.73,1:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.63,1:03:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.63,1:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.64,1:03:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.43,1:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 這麼有感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.03,1:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.54,1:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.85,1:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要噴上去了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.92,1:03:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要弄滿了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.84,1:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個很舒服的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.55,1:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.75,1:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺到了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.82,1:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才舔了那裡 很舒服吧\N我看了就知道
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.03,1:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.89,1:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都這麼硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.29,1:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.33,1:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個淫蕩的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.29,1:05:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.57,1:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.54,1:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.35,1:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不行是什麼意思\N 一別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.39,1:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.09,1:06:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,給我高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.32,1:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮出來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.27,1:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.64,1:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.84,1:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己摸也很舒服吧\N給我繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.32,1:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣哦 你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.50,1:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你聽話
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.83,1:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不會對你動粗的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.54,1:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.10,1:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.54,1:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子摸很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.61,1:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,還要是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.22,1:08:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己摸高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.02,1:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我趴著哦 屁股給我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.23,1:09:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.47,1:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 我要來哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.04,1:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股給我翹起來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.65,1:09:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要弄你淫蕩的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.17,1:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.04,1:10:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.78,1:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股起來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.42,1:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 翹起來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.33,1:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.43,1:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.14,1:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,頂到了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.04,1:10:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,熱熱的小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.06,1:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,翹起來哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.40,1:12:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這麼激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.74,1:12:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說 我反倒想做
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.81,1:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要咽
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.62,1:12:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.74,1:12:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.92,1:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.76,1:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.70,1:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,, 一怎麼了啊 一不要
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.30,1:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那個影片怎麼搞
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.97,1:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,被你同學知道
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.71,1:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被學校發現 被家人發現
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.35,1:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會對你動粗的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.74,1:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還是很不行呢 我來教你\N舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.65,1:14:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.35,1:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微用點力
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.52,1:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那種速度慢慢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.82,1:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,深喉一下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.59,1:15:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.76,1:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.93,1:15:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,, 一難受嗎 一我很難受啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.87,1:15:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.14,1:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再夾 一次哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.50,1:16:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,難受的表情很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.34,1:16:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 舔老師的菊花
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.65,1:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.82,1:16:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,給我舔好了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.31,1:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感受哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.42,1:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,給我含住哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.10,1:17:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.58,1:17:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老師還要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.45,1:17:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.40,1:18:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續用力哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.44,1:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣子 用力才舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.88,1:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.05,1:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.52,1:18:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,用力點
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.71,1:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我來舔你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.55,1:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.92,1:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舔肛門
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.66,1:19:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,菊花
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.83,1:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.53,1:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 屁股翹起來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.02,1:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.82,1:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.03,1:19:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翹起來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.42,1:20:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要 有感覺了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.32,1:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,, 一這樣子很舒服的 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.83,1:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老師很髒的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.65,1:20:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.99,1:20:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.73,1:21:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我來讓你舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.23,1:21:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.33,1:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來 小穴就裂開了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.74,1:21:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.22,1:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.16,1:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.43,1:22:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有 一根手指能插進去
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.33,1:22:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.90,1:22:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老師大肉棒行嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.30,1:22:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.94,1:22:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,, 一感覺要裂開 要忍住哦\N一進不去的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.42,1:22:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.34,1:23:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.01,1:23:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很緊的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.54,1:23:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好浮蕩啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.07,1:23:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.28,1:23:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴去緊了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.82,1:23:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.95,1:23:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴又緊又爽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.43,1:24:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.98,1:24:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.62,1:24:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越舒服了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.94,1:24:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.05,1:25:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,, 一動起來了哦 一不要
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.72,1:25:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,扭腰哦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.29,1:25:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你扭腰
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.29,1:25:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,插進小肉穴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.17,1:25:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.12,1:25:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊的 小穴太小了好緊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.63,1:26:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.86,1:26:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.13,1:26:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來接吻 跟我接吻
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.18,1:26:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.94,1:27:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.81,1:27:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.98,1:27:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,開始摸了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.32,1:27:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.92,1:27:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小肉穴 要插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.01,1:27:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好難受啊 為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.55,1:27:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你太可愛了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.62,1:27:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.42,1:27:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是多麼淫蕩
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.03,1:27:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不是啊 一看你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.53,1:28:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是母豬
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.54,1:28:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好好叫 老師最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.15,1:28:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.45,1:28:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.12,1:29:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.92,1:29:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要KISS
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.12,1:29:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.92,1:30:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,明明不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.82,1:30:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.33,1:30:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 這種事情不行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.93,1:30:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.27,1:30:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子做愛
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.04,1:30:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是很爽的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.08,1:30:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.57,1:30:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.81,1:31:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,, 一那老師來動 一不要不要
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.51,1:31:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候才行
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.99,1:31:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.20,1:31:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.13,1:31:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,, 一動起來了\N 一不要不要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.14,1:31:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小肉穴 太棒了 我的肉棒\N插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.91,1:31:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,, 一就是這樣啊 一不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.60,1:31:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.35,1:32:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.72,1:32:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.23,1:32:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣子哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.85,1:32:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦起來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.09,1:32:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.76,1:32:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.83,1:33:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.33,1:34:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.30,1:34:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.53,1:34:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,給我弄乾淨吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.76,1:35:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以隨便弄啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.46,1:35:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等下回教室
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.13,1:35:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再出現了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.50,1:35:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,被裁員才是我的真心
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.34,1:35:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,回憶起今天 我就足夠幸福了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.05,1:36:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 這傢伙做過了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.52,1:36:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.62,1:36:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,給我老實交代
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.23,1:36:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,已經硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.00,1:36:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.03,1:36:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 這邊來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.31,1:36:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,給我聽話
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.24,1:36:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.95,1:36:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,碧池就要有碧池的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.75,1:36:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己脫掉
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.12,1:36:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別磨磨贈贈的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.96,1:36:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快點脫掉
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.13,1:36:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,自己來做
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.70,1:36:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快脫
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.70,1:36:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,褲子脫掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.08,1:37:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.92,1:37:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲也要脫掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.82,1:37:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.43,1:37:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快點脫掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.53,1:37:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,, 一直看著你的 趕緊脫掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.68,1:37:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看着做 看肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.88,1:37:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.05,1:37:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 如何啊 如何\N感想 看肉棒的感想
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.86,1:37:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.73,1:37:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太大了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.63,1:38:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.57,1:38:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.24,1:38:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.94,1:38:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,, 一怎麼的 一怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.14,1:38:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.91,1:38:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看著這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.55,1:38:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看大肉棒很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.88,1:38:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,, 一很好吃的 一真的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.12,1:38:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,變大了 夾碰 一下 含住
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.03,1:38:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 快點來哦\N別用手碰
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.03,1:38:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,現在摸 快點 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.24,1:38:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.41,1:38:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對著鏡頭來 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.32,1:38:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.63,1:39:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我不要啊 一不能這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.27,1:39:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想派麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.54,1:39:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你舔的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.34,1:39:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快點夾 我說了真希
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.94,1:39:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他看到你微笑 就說你很美
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.15,1:39:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,才發現你很可愛 他知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.32,1:39:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,, 一真是囉嗦啊\N 一剛才說什麼不要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.73,1:39:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 嘴巴張開
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.20,1:39:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.22,1:40:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔哦
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.73,1:40:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要 進不去的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.73,1:40:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子啊 用臉來做
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.03,1:40:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.84,1:40:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比我還大啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.44,1:40:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 這麼大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.81,1:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊來舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.65,1:40:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 眼睛看著
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.09,1:40:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.62,1:40:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.63,1:40:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.30,1:40:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.27,1:40:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,舔到就對了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.34,1:41:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你快點 發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.75,1:41:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你很愛他的吧 一對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.39,1:41:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋也要好好弄
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.04,1:41:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好好弄哦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.04,1:41:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭髮出聲音哦 快點動
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.95,1:41:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.69,1:41:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,, 一很舒服吧 一真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.66,1:41:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.63,1:41:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 蛋蛋也可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.04,1:42:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋吸進去哦 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.55,1:42:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,右邊 還有右邊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.72,1:42:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服叮阿
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.63,1:42:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.30,1:43:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續來吸住
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.24,1:43:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊說抱歉 再來
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.74,1:43:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你說出抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.64,1:43:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.95,1:43:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.85,1:43:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.23,1:43:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.27,1:43:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續來舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.17,1:43:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.94,1:43:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,, 一抱歉啊\N 一給我含著說好好說
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.31,1:43:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好好說對不起 含著說
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.55,1:43:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快點哦 就是這樣 含住了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.32,1:43:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.83,1:44:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快點說出來哦 知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.03,1:44:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,給我道歉 聽到沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.30,1:44:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.74,1:44:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續 道歉含著哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.88,1:44:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.69,1:44:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.86,1:44:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.74,1:44:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.24,1:44:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.02,1:45:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你很熟練的哦 很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.83,1:45:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,別停下來 繼續來啊 聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.93,1:45:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.80,1:45:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.64,1:45:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺太刺激了對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.81,1:45:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,深一點
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.18,1:45:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.63,1:46:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這是服務 看看你的奶子
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.63,1:46:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不然射不出來的 含著
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.31,1:46:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,單手握著 趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.82,1:46:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.09,1:46:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.72,1:46:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.49,1:46:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.50,1:46:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣子舔薯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.22,1:47:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.42,1:47:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一點哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.30,1:47:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,舔著來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.37,1:47:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,夾住哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.67,1:47:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.15,1:47:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.83,1:47:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,, 一好難受 一是的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.03,1:48:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼難受就對了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.63,1:48:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴露出來等著
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.97,1:48:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等下要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.44,1:48:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.65,1:48:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 大肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.42,1:48:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最後打開嘴巴等著哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.53,1:48:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.40,1:48:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續來哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.94,1:48:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了哦 嘴巴張開哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.64,1:48:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我射了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.54,1:49:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 弄乾浮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.33,1:50:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.23,1:50:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.24,1:50:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們為什麼沒發現呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.98,1:50:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.81,1:50:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,眼鏡摘掉就是大美女
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.69,1:50:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到騙過了我們
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.29,1:50:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,眼鏡摘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.93,1:50:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到了有趣的事情\N 一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.77,1:50:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.84,1:50:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.64,1:50:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.65,1:51:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽要回夾了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.78,1:51:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.16,1:51:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.33,1:51:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.10,1:51:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.07,1:51:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這身打扮
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.34,1:51:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這身打扮 看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.24,1:51:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.44,1:51:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,還尚俊這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.98,1:51:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,變不錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.25,1:51:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你也來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.22,1:51:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,讓身體放鬆
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.26,1:51:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對對的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.59,1:51:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,, 一不要 一囉嗦讓我們摸
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.46,1:51:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身材不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.44,1:52:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面也要哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.41,1:52:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.75,1:52:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,還能繼續的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.31,1:52:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看了身體
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.85,1:52:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.42,1:52:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,, 一感覺有點意思哦 一是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.73,1:52:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.63,1:52:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,興奮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.73,1:52:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再來更害羞的姿勢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.03,1:52:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.14,1:52:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.40,1:52:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 是不是濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.24,1:52:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯哦 很濕的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.91,1:52:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.31,1:52:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,, 一濕透了啊 一看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.29,1:52:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.16,1:53:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你在做什麼啊 一幹嚇
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.73,1:53:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.84,1:53:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是生過孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.54,1:53:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.24,1:53:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.55,1:53:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太刺激了吧 綠色的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.65,1:53:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好啊 來摸吧很好
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.52,1:53:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴摸一下 好緊的洞□啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.13,1:53:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.43,1:53:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.27,1:53:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.84,1:53:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.11,1:53:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股真不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.65,1:53:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不錯啊 好厲害的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.92,1:53:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很榛的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.92,1:54:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫蕩的姿勢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.53,1:54:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,來更色的姿勢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.46,1:54:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,趴薯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.33,1:54:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,夾吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.63,1:54:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夾吧 給我趴著哦 趴著
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.54,1:54:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯的 如何啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.78,1:54:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.55,1:54:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們看看你的臉哦 再來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.52,1:54:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.72,1:54:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼可愛的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.23,1:54:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這是誰的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.63,1:54:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,, 一是真希的\N 一拿過來很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.87,1:54:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.24,1:54:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡優君吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.54,1:54:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.11,1:54:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我知道的 一不是
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.35,1:55:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你打給他
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.92,1:55:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,, 一打給他 聽到沒 一親愛的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.82,1:55:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.13,1:55:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,打給他吧 快點
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.87,1:55:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.44,1:55:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,, 一優君 一怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.58,1:55:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,突然打給你不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.32,1:55:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,, 一讓我看看你的臉\N 一還以為是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.72,1:55:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想聽你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.12,1:55:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.96,1:55:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,做作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.37,1:55:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,作業加油哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.13,1:55:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.64,1:55:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在鍛煉身體哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.74,1:56:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 很少見的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.95,1:56:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.05,1:56:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯的 怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.32,1:56:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.73,1:56:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 信號不好
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.73,1:56:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.20,1:56:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的咽
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.97,1:56:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在鍛煉是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.31,1:56:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.71,1:56:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺還行吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.15,1:56:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.72,1:56:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你跟老師一起
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.73,1:56:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.17,1:56:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我找他有事情的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.90,1:57:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,, 一還有升學的事情 一這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.81,1:57:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.85,1:57:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.42,1:57:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼在喘氣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.86,1:57:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.50,1:57:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.33,1:57:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被其他人聽到的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.33,1:57:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就很煩惱
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.64,1:57:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.81,1:57:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那你沒事吧現在
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.74,1:57:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,現在在做激烈運動
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.02,1:57:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,, 一我知道了 一不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.59,1:57:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,, 一你沒事吧 一沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.50,1:58:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,下次啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.33,1:58:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起來玩吧
